<div class="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row"  >
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
        <h3 class="text-primary text-center"><b> What is STUDY HALL</b></h3> 
        <h4 style = "line-height: 1.5em" >
          - In support of Women & Minorities in Tech: Mentor, Network, Improve Skills <br> 
          - Hang out in video chat with other people learning topics you're interested in - we're currently working on Web Development topics related to building ThinQ.tv, a Woman Owned Tech Startup <br>
          - Peers and possibly mentors are there while you're working incase you have questions or need someone to bounce ideas, pair program <br>
          - Or work quietly in the chat room to be there for each other when that Aha moment happens
         </h4>          
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
        <div class="row" id="countdown_clock">
          <%= render 'layouts/countdown_clockstudy' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="row" id="countdown_clock">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12">
      <h2>Study Hall Schedule</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <br>Don't see your desired hour on the schedule yet? <br>
            <%= link_to 'Post Study Hall Hour', new_event_path, class: "btn btn-warning", title: "Host drop-in Study Hall sessions or invite people to ask questions about your area of expertise" %>
          <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tabContainer">
    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12"> 
      <div class="buttonContainer">
        <button onclick="showPanel(0,'#f44336')">List View </button>
        <button onclick="showPanel(1,'#4caf50')">Monthly View </button>
        <!-- <button onclick="showPanel(2,'#2196f3')">Weekly View</button> -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tabPanel">
      <div class="row" id="calendar"> 
        <div class="col-xs-12"> 
          <%= render 'layouts/maincalendar', collection: @events %> 
        </div>   
      </div> 
    </div>
    <div class="tabPanel" >
       <%= render 'layouts/monthcalendar', collection: @eventsAll %>
    </div> 
  </div>

    <h2 class="text-center text-primary"><b>
      <span>We currently have Study Halls for 3 topics:</span> </b>
    </h2>
    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div>
          <div>
            <%= image_tag("marketing.jpg", :class => "img-squares")%>
              <!-- marketing: https://unsplash.com/photos/wD1LRb9OeEo   -->
          </div>          
            <div>
             <h4 class = "bg-primary text-center lead"> UX RESEARCH <br> </h4>
            </div>
          </div>
              <div class = "text-center">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#first">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down"></span>
                </button>
                <div class = "collapse" id = "first">
                  <p class = "text-left lead">
                 We currently have a group meeting several times per week to work on survey questions related to the ThinQ.tv site. The purpose of the UX Research Study Hall is to:
                 <br>
                  - Be in the video chat viewer for each other incase you want feedback from others with UX career interests.<br>
                  - Form a support group available several hours per day who are there when you want to be around others also improving their UX Survey skills.
                  </p>
                
                </div> <!-- Collapse content -->
              
              </div> <!-- Make center -->
            
      </div> <!-- end of first pic-->
      

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div>
          <div>
              <%= image_tag("ruby.jpg", :class => "img-squares")%>
              <!-- ruby: https://unsplash.com/photos/yktK2qaiVHI   -->
          </div>
            <div>
                  <h4 class = "bg-primary text-center lead"> RUBY ON RAILS Web Development <br> </h4>
            </div>
          </div>
              <div class = "text-center">

                <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#second">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down"></span>
                </button>
                <div class = "collapse" id = "second">
                  <p class = "text-left lead">
                  Front and back end developers can co-work or co-hack with each other. The purpose of the Rails Study Hall is to:<br>
                  - Be in the video chat viewer for each other incase you have Rails questions while working on your project.<br>
                  - Form a support group available several hours per day who are there when you want to be around others also improving their Rails skills.<br><br>
                  Several of us are working with the existing code base for ThinQ.tv to learn Ruby on Rails. Our repository is at https://github.com/ece106/tomatocan if you'd like to learn Rails by contributing to ThinQ.tv's code, the first step is to fork & clone the repository. Drop in to Study Hall hours and ask us how to join our Discord channel and find the list of tasks to work on.
                  </p>
                </div> <!-- Collapse content -->              
              </div> <!-- Make center -->
            
      </div> <!-- end of second pic-->

      <div class="container col-md-4">
        <div>
          <div>
            <%= image_tag("uidesign.jpg", :class => "img-squares")%>
              <!-- uidesign: https://unsplash.com/photos/WYwT7pXuXvo  -->
          </div>
            <div>
                  <h4 class = "bg-primary text-center lead"> Women Developers <br> </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
          <div class = "text-center">

                <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#third">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down"></span>
                </button>
                <div class = "collapse" id = "third">
                  <p class = "text-left lead">
                  ThinQ.tv's founder, Lisa Schaefer, earned all 3 of her engineering degrees at Arizona State University. The purpose of our Women Developers Study Hall is to: <br>
                  - Meet other female developers from around the US <br>
                  - Support each other<br>
                  - Bring #metoo issues we all face out in the open without backlash for doing so<br>
                  </p>
                </div> <!-- Collapse content -->              
              </div> <!-- Make center -->            
      </div> <!-- end of third pic-->

    <script type="text/javascript">
      showPanel(0,'#f44336');
    </script>
